      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be verified under a documented QA plan with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under an FDA-recognized QA framework. Version control, regression test suite, and change logs are maintained. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
