      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification activities must confirm correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark problems.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity and pipe flow were solved and compared against analytical solutions. Errors within 0.5% confirming correct numerical implementation."
