      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match the simulated operating envelope within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments conducted at 5 flow-speed combinations (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) matching the COU operating envelope. Fluid temperature and hematocrit controlled to within ±2% of target values."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
